member.example:
This sample shows how to call GetWidgetsAsync with required parameters and parse the result.

var client = new WidgetManagerClient();

await foreach (var data in client.GetWidgetsAsync())
{
    JsonElement result = JsonDocument.Parse(data.ToStream()).RootElement;
    Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("name").ToString());
    Console.WriteLine(result.GetProperty("manufacturerId").ToString());
}

member.remarks:
Below is the JSON schema for one item in the pageable response.
Response Body:
Schema for Array: { name: string, # Required. The widget name. manufacturerId: string, # Required. The ID of the widget's manufacturer. }

